The paper focuses on visual tracking, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed framework involves camera movement and trajectory prediction, which are related to robotics (cs.RO). The collaborative correlation filter (CCF) is a machine learning technique, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
